<div class="indent"><strong>Mulder:</strong> It's not a bad piece of ash, huh? <br><em>[Scully gives him a look]</em> <br><strong>Mulder:</strong> The bat... <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ThatCameOutWrong" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ThatCameOutWrong">I'm talking about the bat.</a>
