</div><div class="indent"><strong>Karen Page:</strong> <em>[giggling]</em> Sunk the eight-ball.
</div><div class="indent"><strong>Matt Murdock:</strong> <em>[grins]</em> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DoubleEntendre" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DoubleEntendre">Well, something went in...</a>
</div><div class="indent"><strong>Karen Page:</strong> I tell you what, you boys re-rack. I will, uh, buy rounds for the rematch. <em>[Karen heads off to the counter; an annoyed Foggy turns to Matt]</em>
