<div class="indent"><strong>Nick:</strong> Oh, no, you're doing it all wrong. Here, let me show you. No, no, no. I've been doing this for years. See, the way to pick up a mug is like that. You just got to relax into it. <br><strong>Jess:</strong> He wasn't doing that! <br><strong>Nick:</strong> That's exactly what he was doing.
