<h2 class="bold font-l">The Definition of "Yum-Yum"</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Sugarpuss tells Bertram that she thinks that he is a &quot;yum-yum&quot; type and decides to demonstrate what it means. (Most likely means &quot;kissable&quot;) </p>
</div>
